snippet.title: Highwater - Official Cinematic Trailer | Future Games Show 2023
snippet.description:
Highwater is a turn-based strategy adventure game about a flooded Earth making the entire planet doomed. Players will guide Nikos and his friends through the flooded world for the potential to fight for a chance at an escape. Highwater is launching in Summer 2023 for PlayStation 5, Xbox Series S|X, Nintendo Switch, and PC.

#GameTrailers #SoG #Gaming
